parameters: $gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuFlEx>.I’ve got a few talents up my sleeve.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeAnDe^.Just how much time are we going to kill down here?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuFlEx>.We’ve got to wait out the heat, sugarplum.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "H1FlEx.At least we got plenty of booze.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuFlDe>.The Guild is ours for the taking.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "H2FlEx.A toast to Helmer! Our fearless leader!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuBaEx>.That amulet was worth more money than you, Victor.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuFlEx>.No… That thief gave us the motivation we needed to take what is rightfully ours.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HwAnDe.And now Wilkes is dead! Good riddance!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuFlEx>.Soon, everything that was stolen from me will be back in my possession and the Guild will be led by one man.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeBaDe^.An incredible feat. You’ve killed half of our members somehow.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuAnEx>.A weapon fell onto my lap. The purge was necessary. Don’t you agree?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "H1AnDe.Sometimes I wonder if Nellie shares our same loyalty.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuAnOp>.What the fuck did you just say?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuMaEx>.You keep your god-damn mouth shut or I’ll staple it shut.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "H2HaEx.Come on, boss. I made peanut butter cookies.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeAnDe.I can’t stand it here. I’m going back out.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "H1AnEx.The boss hates it when you leave.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeShCl.What the fuck are you doing here? What is she doing here?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeAnEx.I told you to stop following me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeAnEx.You dumb fucks. I’m working for Kimura. You aren’t supposed to be here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeMaEx.No one, and I mean no one is supposed to know I’m a mole. You have to get out of here now.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeAnOp.You’re in no position to be demanding anything from me, detective.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.If she wasn’t working with us, she’d have already called for help.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeAnOp.If they find out about me, I won’t be the only one losing their head…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeAnEx.There are agents infiltrating the entire Guild… Kimura has an entire team.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeAnCl.Shit. You aren’t supposed to know. She’s going to flip her lid.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HwPaCl^.Oh, god. I think I’m going to throw up.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HwAnOp.Hey! Who the hell is that woman?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeAnEx>.If you must know. She’s my girlfriend… Vanessa.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeFlEx@>.Come on, Vanessa. I want you to meet someone.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McMcWoEx#>.Go on. Smooth talk her. She’s drunk.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeFlEx>.Vanessa, this is Phyliss Daggett. One badass thief.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HwFlDe.Maybe I had you all wrong, Nellie. I thought you were choking down Duncan’s dick.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HwFlEx.If you’re a muff diver, that changes everything.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeFlEx>.I love eating pussy. Chicks are my thing. Men… are gross.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeAnEx>.Come on and sit down, Phyliss. You’re going to fall.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuAnEx>.And don’t get blood on the carpet. I hate it when you get blood on the carpet.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HwAnOp.Good riddance. That guy gives me the creeps.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeAnEx>.You heard the man. Go get a gun. And make it fast.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "H1AnEx.But the guns are on the other side of the facility. Let’s just choke him out.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "H1AnEx.I’m not doing it. You do it!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "H1AnEx.We’ll be back in 8 minutes. Are you okay alone?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "H2AnOp.What? Toward the piano? That’ll make him even more mad.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "H1AnOp>.Don’t you know what the hell you’re doing?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "H2AnEx.If you’re so smart, why don’t you shoot him.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "H1FlEx>.Don’t worry. I won’t get blood anywhere…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeAnEx.What are you doing? Go after him!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeFlEx.I’ll tell them you’re some sort of Houdini.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.I need to get the hell away from here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.Shit… Did they really take my amulet?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnOp.What the hell took you so long?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.I had to be sure I did it right.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeAnEx.You all have caused enough trouble. You have to get out of here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.What about the drunk lady? She’s going to wake up soon.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeAnEx.Stay away from me. You’re going to blow my cover.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeWoEx.Don’t let Kimura know you saw me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.Somehow I think that is out of my hands at this point.");
